---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Button from '../../components/Button.astro';
import SectionDivider from '../../components/SectionDivider.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<BaseLayout title="Leadership Circle — Gregory the Great Institute" description="Strategic partners shaping the future of Catholic culture in Canada. $5,000+/year.">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero-lc section--dark">
    <div class="hero-lc__bg" style={`background-image: url(${base}images/art/school-of-athens.jpg)`}></div>
    <div class="hero-lc__overlay"></div>
    <div class="hero-lc__content container">
      <p class="label text-gold">Strategic Partnership</p>
      <h1 class="display">The Leadership Circle</h1>
      <p class="hero-lc__subtitle">For those who see what Catholic culture in Canada could become — and are ready to build it.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Vision -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container lc-intro reveal">
      <p class="lc-intro__lead">
        The Leadership Circle is not a giving tier. It is a <strong>strategic partnership</strong>
        with the people building the future of Catholic intellectual life in Canada.
      </p>
      <p>
        Leadership Circle members don't just fund programs — they shape them. They sit at the table
        where decisions are made about what the Institute builds next. A Catholic trade school for
        young men. Certificate programs in Christian leadership. A national think-tank that equips
        Catholics to engage the culture with confidence. These are not distant dreams. They are the
        next phase — and they require partners who share the vision and have the capacity to make
        it real.
      </p>
      <p>
        If that describes you, Dr. Topping would welcome a personal conversation.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <SectionDivider />

  <!-- What Leadership Looks Like -->
  <section class="section section--linen">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <p class="label text-gold">What It Looks Like</p>
        <h2>Partnership, Not Patronage</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="lc-features reveal-stagger">
        <div class="lc-feature reveal">
          <div class="lc-feature__accent"></div>
          <div class="lc-feature__body">
            <h3>Patron Advisory Council</h3>
            <p>
              A seat on the advisory body that helps Dr. Topping and the Board shape the Institute's
              strategic direction. Your experience, network, and counsel — applied directly.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="lc-feature reveal">
          <div class="lc-feature__accent"></div>
          <div class="lc-feature__body">
            <h3>Co-Naming of a Major Program</h3>
            <p>
              Name a flagship initiative — a masterclass series, a research program, a conference
              track — in your name, your family's name, or in honour of someone who shaped your faith.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="lc-feature reveal">
          <div class="lc-feature__accent"></div>
          <div class="lc-feature__body">
            <h3>Annual Leadership Retreat</h3>
            <p>
              A private gathering with Dr. Topping, the Board, and fellow Leadership Circle members.
              Deep conversation about the state of Catholic culture, the Institute's trajectory,
              and the work ahead.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="lc-feature reveal">
          <div class="lc-feature__accent"></div>
          <div class="lc-feature__body">
            <h3>Quarterly Strategic Briefings</h3>
            <p>
              Written updates from Dr. Topping on what's working, what's changing, and what's coming.
              The information that shapes your confidence in the partnership.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The 2027 Vision -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container lc-vision reveal">
      <div class="section-header">
        <p class="label text-gold">The Road Ahead</p>
        <h2>What Year Three Makes Possible</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="lc-vision__body">
        <p>
          In its first year, the Institute proved the mission is real. In Year Two, we are scaling
          what works — more Book Studies, a second Magnalia issue, expanded masterclasses, and the
          second Renewing Culture Conference.
        </p>
        <p>
          Year Three is where the Institute becomes an institution. The programs that are proving
          themselves now become permanent infrastructure:
        </p>
        <ul class="lc-vision__list">
          <li><strong>A Catholic trade school</strong> — practical formation for young men in the skilled trades, grounded in the virtues</li>
          <li><strong>Certificate programs</strong> — credentialed courses in Christian leadership, Catholic social teaching, and classical education</li>
          <li><strong>A national think-tank</strong> — original research equipping Catholics to engage public policy, culture, and media with confidence</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          These are not ideas on a whiteboard. They are in active planning, with timelines, budgets,
          and the institutional credibility to execute. What they require is partners with the vision
          and capacity to build alongside us.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <SectionDivider />

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="section section--dark lc-cta-section">
    <div class="container lc-cta">
      <h2>Let's Talk</h2>
      <p>
        Leadership Circle partnerships begin with a personal conversation with Dr. Topping.
        No pressure. No pitch deck. Just a direct conversation about what you care about
        and how the Institute's vision aligns with yours.
      </p>
      <div class="lc-cta__price">
        <span class="lc-cta__amount">$5,000+</span>
        <span class="lc-cta__period">/year</span>
      </div>
      <Button href={`${base}contact/`} variant="primary">Request a Conversation</Button>
      <p class="lc-cta__ff">
        For visionary partners building the 2027 Launch: <strong>Founding Fellow — $25,000+/year</strong>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="text-align: center; padding: 24px 0 48px;">
    <a href={`${base}support/`} class="back-link">← Back to All Giving Options</a>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* Hero */
  .hero-lc {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 400px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-lc__bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center 30%;
  }

  .hero-lc__overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(14, 51, 82, 0.72), rgba(14, 51, 82, 0.90));
  }

  .hero-lc__content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 720px;
    margin-inline: auto;
    padding-block: 60px;
  }

  .hero-lc__content h1 {
    color: var(--color-text-on-dark);
    margin: 8px 0 12px;
  }

  .hero-lc__subtitle {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 1.12rem;
    color: rgba(245, 239, 229, 0.85);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* Intro */
  .lc-intro {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }

  .lc-intro__lead {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 1.12rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--color-ink);
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  .lc-intro p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--color-gray);
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  .lc-intro p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

  /* Section header */
  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-component);
  }

  .section-header h2 { margin-top: 8px; }

  /* Features */
  .lc-features {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 16px;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }

  .lc-feature {
    display: flex;
    background-color: var(--color-parchment);
    border: 1px solid rgba(90, 90, 110, 0.08);
    border-radius: 3px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .lc-feature__accent {
    width: 5px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    background-color: var(--color-gold);
  }

  .lc-feature__body {
    padding: 24px 20px;
  }

  .lc-feature h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-navy);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .lc-feature p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-gray);
  }

  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .lc-features { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  }

  /* Vision */
  .lc-vision__body {
    max-width: 680px;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }

  .lc-vision__body p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--color-gray);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .lc-vision__list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
    margin: 20px 0;
    padding-left: 0;
  }

  .lc-vision__list li {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-gray);
    padding-left: 20px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .lc-vision__list li::before {
    content: '—';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-gold);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .lc-vision__list li strong {
    color: var(--color-navy);
  }

  /* CTA */
  .lc-cta {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 560px;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }

  .lc-cta h2 {
    color: var(--color-text-on-dark);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .lc-cta > p:first-of-type {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: rgba(245, 239, 229, 0.85);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .lc-cta__price { margin-bottom: 24px; }

  .lc-cta__amount {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text-on-dark);
  }

  .lc-cta__period {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: rgba(245, 239, 229, 0.6);
  }

  .lc-cta__ff {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: rgba(245, 239, 229, 0.5);
    margin-top: 20px;
    padding-top: 16px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(245, 239, 229, 0.1);
  }

  .lc-cta__ff strong {
    color: var(--color-gold);
  }

  .back-link {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-gold);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .back-link:hover { color: var(--color-crimson); }

  .section--linen { background-color: var(--color-linen); }
</style>
